705716f-a.title: Brooklyn: Middleton Street - Throop Avenue
705716f-a.text:
166-190 Middleton Street, south side, east of Throop (left) to
Harrison Aves. (right), as seen across excavation for the Independent
Subway, (City owned) from Lynch Street.
March 24, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
